 (47563007), <a href="/web/20180712182858/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0162429&amp;fLockTerm=Nutritional+deficiency+state">Nutritional deficiency state</a>
 (65404009), <a href="/web/20180712182858/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0162429&amp;fLockTerm=Nutritional+deficiency+state">Nutritional deficiency state</a>
 (70241007), <a href="/web/20180712182858/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C1443923&amp;fLockTerm=Oral+rehydration+solution">Oral rehydration solution</a>
 (409585005), <a href="/web/20180712182858/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0029168&amp;fLockTerm=Oral+rehydration+therapy">Oral rehydration therapy</a>
